TextArea_GetSelection
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Window=>window/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<textarea_get_selection_text>
Syntax:	TextArea_GetSelection
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
     bit 0 set:   return text.
     bit 0 unset: return indexes.
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 0x4018 + 6 (16414)
r3 = gadget component Id
r4 = pointer to buffer
r5 = size of buffer
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r5 = size of buffer required (if r4=0)
     else r4 points to text.
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method gets the selected text in the TextArea.